Final project - Yuriy Toporovskyy, Mostapha Mohammed

A table hockey game where you play against multiple computers!
Everyone starts with 20 lives. If you reach 0, you lose. 

Functionality: 
- Drag with LMB: move your paddle.

- [N/n] : New game

- [1..3] : New game and select difficulty.

- [P/s] : Pause and unpause

- [Q/q/ESC] : Quit game

- Right click menu: Provides new game, pause and unpause functionality as well.
